{"type":"text","timestamp":1782577139488,"sessionID":"ses_0f62aa824ffeaYjaCmpYi13tcz","part":{"id":"prt_f09e0559e002blinR7qdPkIi6f","messageID":"msg_f09e04aed001zAu06yWnj562XL","sessionID":"ses_0f62aa824ffeaYjaCmpYi13tcz","type":"text","text":"Implemented the phase-03 onboarding/login evidence batch and updated the phase authority rows.\n\nChanged files:\n- `Foodike-Harmony/entry/src/test/cangjie/phase03_onboarding_login_profile_test.cj`: expanded focused phase-03 tests to cover onboarding slide order/content/media and login credential/message contracts.\n- `translation-inputs/source-coverage-matrix.json`: closed 22 phase-03 onboarding/login rows through the authority patch tool with concrete `implemented` or `not-applicable` evidence.\n- `translation-inputs/source-coverage-matrix.md`: synced automatically by the authority patch tool.\n- `translation-inputs/phase03_matrix_patch.json`: temporary authority patch payload used to update the matrix.\n\nCommands run:\n- `cjpm test` in `Foodike-Harmony/entry`\n- `python D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\search_v3.py \"ArkUI Cangjie TextInput password input obscure text\" --mode api --json --limit 5`\n- `python D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\search_v3.py \"TextInput password icon showPassword ArkUI Cangjie\" --mode api --json --limit 5`\n- `python D:\\X2Cangjie\\X2Cangjie\\scripts\\shared\\source_coverage\\patch_authority.py --kind matrix --authority D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\source-coverage-matrix.json --patch D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\phase03_matrix_patch.json --markdown D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\source-coverage-matrix.md --plan-json D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\plan.json --target-project D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\Foodike-Harmony`\n- `git status --short`\n\nBuild result:\n- NOT RUN for the phase build gate.\n- Test harness reproduction FAIL:\n  `cjpm test` from `Foodike-Harmony/entry` fails before phase tests run because the root package imports `kit.ArkUI`, `kit.AbilityKit`, and `ohos.resource` without matching dependencies in `entry/cjpm.toml`.\n- Existing verification evidence still shows phase-01 and phase-02 build gate PASS only.\n\nPlan changes:\n- none\n\nDeferred issues:\n- Phase-03 focused tests are present but not runnable yet because the current root `entry` package test wiring is blocked by missing package dependencies in `entry/cjpm.toml`.\n- I did not force a password-mask code change in `login_page.cj` because the indexed Cangjie docs I checked did not give a clear current-SDK password modifier name. The source parity gap remains worth addressing once a concrete ArkUI Cangjie API is confirmed.\n- The workspace is already dirty with many unrelated generated/build/report changes; I did not touch or revert those.\n\nWhat I updated in coverage:\n- Closed actual onboarding/login behavior as `implemented` with concrete endpoints:\n  - login authentication/session handoff\n  - login route navigation to home\n  - login observable state propagation\n  - onboarding slide data loading/order\n  - onboarding pager progression and final navigation to login\n  - onboarding observable page-index driven UI behavior\n- Closed analyzer over-detections as `not-applicable` with source-backed evidence:\n  - login image-viewer/zoom\n  - login notification/widget\n  - login/onboarding permission rows\n  - login settings/toggles rows\n  - `LoginViewModel` lifecycle/permission false positives\n  - `FoodikeTextField` permission/settings false positives\n\nNext recommended action:\n- Fix the target test harness/package wiring for `entry` and `entry/src/test/cangjie`, then rerun the phase-03 test gate so the new onboarding/login tests can count as compile/run evidence instead of `harness-blocked`.","time":{"start":1782577124766,"end":1782577139486}}}
